headline: Welcome to the Meme Market
summary: Take Palantir, the defense-technology company whose shares have more than doubled this year.  Alex Karp, Palantir’s eccentric leader, is known as “Daddy Karp” to many of the company’s followers who call themselves “Palantarians.”  Michael Saylor, leader of crypto-buying machine Strategy, has a similar playbook.
